<p>
  <big>Other Options:</big><br/><br/>
<i>* Use toolbar image<br/></i>
  <small>
  This option allows you to change the backround behind the toolbar buttons. Select a valid image by
  clicking on the &#x22;Browse&#x22; button. To use WinWAP without an image behind the buttons you
  should remove the check from this option.
  </small>
<br/><br/>

<i>* Fonts and colors<br/></i>
  <small>
  With these settings you can select the font used to display the WAP pages, and the color of the text
  and background. You can also effect the size of the text with the &#x22;Size of text&#x22; selection
  box. Note that if you are using a background image the background color is not visible
  </small>
<br/><br/>

<do label="Back"> <prev/> </do>
</p>
